quran[17{c,v,t}:
52,15,ab batao yeh jaadoo hai ya tumhe soojh nahi raha hai ?
52,16,"jao ab jhulso iss ke andar, tum khuwa sabr karo ya nah karo, tumahray liye yaksaa hai, tumhe waisa hi badla diya ja raha hai jaisay tum amal kar rahay thay"
52,17,mut-taqi log wahan baghoon aur nematon mein hon ge
52,18,"lutaf le rahay hon ge unn cheezon se jo unn ka rab inhen day ga, aur unn ka rab unhen dozakh ke azaab se bacha le ga"
52,19,( un se kaha jaye ga ) khao aur piyo mazay se apne unn aamaal ke siilay mein jo tum karte rahay ho
52,20,woh aamnay samnay bichay hue takhton par takiye lagaye baithy hon ge aur hum khobsorat aankhon wali hooren unn se bayah den ge
52,21,jo log imaan laaye hain aur unn ki aulaad bhi kisi darja imaan mein un ke naqsh qadam par chali hai un ki uss aulaad ko bhi hum ( jannat mein ) unn ke sath mila den ge aur unn ke amal mein koi ghata un ko nah den ge har shakhs apne ksb ke aiwz rehan hai
52,22,"hum unn ko har terhan ke phal aur gosht, jis cheez ko bhi un ka jee chahay ga, khoob diye chalay jayen ge"
52,23,wahan woh aik dosray se jaam sharaab lapak lapak kar le rahay hon ge jis mein nah yawa goi hogi nah bad kirdari
52,24,aur unn ki khidmat mein woh larke dorrtay phir rahay hon ge jo unhi ke liye makhsoos hon ge aisay khobsorat jaisay chhupa kar rakhay hue moti
52,25,yeh log aapas mein aik dosray se ( duniya mein guzray hue ) halaat poucheen ge
52,26,yeh kahin ge ke hum pehlay apne ghar walon mein drtay hue zindagi busr karte thay
52,27,aakhir-kaar Allah ne hum par fazl farmaya aur hamein jhalsa dainay wali howa ke azaab se bacha liya
52,28,"hum pichli zindagi mein usi se duayen mangte thay, woh waqai bara hi mohsin aur Raheem hai"
52,29,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum nasiyaat kiye jao, apne rab ke fazl se nah tum کاہن ho aur nah Majnoon"
52,30,kya yeh log kehte hain ke yeh shakhs shayar hai jis ke haq mein hum gardish ayyaam ka intzaar kar rahay hain ?
52,31,"inn se kaho acha intzaar karo, mein bhi tumahray sath intzaar karta hon"
